        Nearest City:


   Site Amenities:

     Restroom - Vault

                          Boat Launch Type:

                            1 Concrete Ramp

   Car Parking Facilities:

     15 Gravel Spaces

                          Trailer Parking Facilities:

                            15 Gravel Spaces

        Seasonal Limitations:

        No known limitations

        Tidal or Water Limitations:

        No known limitations

        Driving Directions:

        From Shelton, N on SR 3, 3.5 mi; L on McEwan Prairie Rd 1 mi; R on
        Mason Lake Rd; go to St. Andrews Dr.; go .5 mi; ramp on E side of
        Rd.
        Site Description:

        The boat ramp is narrow and developing erosion on both sides. There
        is a sign that states that the use of the boat ramp is for fishing
