        From Belfair, W on SR 300 12 mi; R on Belfair-Tahuya Rd, go 4 mi; L
        on Dewatto Rd, go 2 mi; L on gravel Rd; go 1.2 mi. Site is to R.
        Site Description:

        The boat ramp has a steep grade at the shoreline and the surface is
        uneven. The site also has eight campsites and picnic tables.
        Registration is required to camp, but there is no fee.


