   Up Arrow to Map   35. Panther Lake - Mason (WDFW)

        Waterbody: Panther Lake (Mason Co.)
        Site Manager: Fish & Wildlife Dept of
        Nearest City:


   Site Amenities:

     Restroom - Vault

                          Boat Launch Type:

                            1 Gravel Ramp

   Car Parking Facilities:

     10 Gravel Spaces

                          Trailer Parking Facilities:

                            10 Gravel Spaces

        Seasonal Limitations:

        No known limitations

        Tidal or Water Limitations:

        yes - site is open from the end of April through October.

        Driving Directions:

        From Belfair, N on Old Belfair Highway 3.6 mi; R on Belfair-Dewatto
        Rd, go 4 mi; turn R at "Public Fishing" sign.
